---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
import Schedule from '../../components/Schedule';
---

<Base title="BJJ (Gi)" description="Brazilian Jiu-Jitsu Gi classes at Lions MMA Vancouver. Led by black belts Guilherme Falcao, Gabrielle Stan, Alberto Garcia, and Lucio Tavares.">

  <!-- Full-width hero image with text overlay -->
  <div class="relative w-full h-[280px] md:h-[520px] overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Image placeholder (swap for real <img> when photos arrive) -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-iron/60 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-3">
      <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-smoke/20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M23 19a2 2 0 01-2 2H3a2 2 0 01-2-2V8a2 2 0 012-2h4l2-3h6l2 3h4a2 2 0 012 2v11z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/><circle cx="12" cy="13" r="4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/></svg>
      <p class="font-mono text-[10px] tracking-widest text-smoke/30 uppercase">Image Coming Soon</p>
    </div>
    <!-- Dark overlay so text is readable -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-void/50"></div>
    <!-- Nav spacer + text pinned to bottom-left -->
    <div class="relative z-10 h-full flex flex-col justify-end pb-14 px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-20 max-w-7xl mx-auto w-full" style="padding-top: 96px;">
      <p class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-canvas/60 mb-4">THE GENTLE ART</p>
      <h1 class="font-display text-[clamp(3.5rem,7vw,7rem)] uppercase tracking-tight text-canvas leading-none">BJJ (GI).</h1>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Content -->
  <div class="py-24 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">

    <!-- What it is -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 mb-24">
      <div>
        <p class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-smoke border-b border-iron pb-2 mb-8">WHAT IT IS</p>
        <div class="space-y-6 font-body text-canvas/80 leading-relaxed">
          <p>Brazilian Jiu-Jitsu is a ground fighting system built on one premise: technique neutralizes size. A well-trained smaller person can control, submit, and survive against a much larger untrained opponent. That is not marketing copy. It is the central truth that makes BJJ unique among martial arts, and the reason it has become the foundation of every serious combat sport competitor's game.</p>
          <p>Gi BJJ adds a layer of complexity through the use of the traditional kimono. Grips on the collar, lapels, and sleeves create control options and submission setups that do not exist in No-Gi. It rewards patience, precision, and a deep understanding of leverage. The Gi slows things down enough that the technical gaps become impossible to ignore, which makes it the best classroom for learning the art properly.</p>
          <p>The grappling staff at Lions is among the strongest in Vancouver. Guilherme Falcao (Black Belt, 1st Degree), Gabrielle Stan (Black Belt), Alberto Garcia (Black Belt), and Lucio Tavares (Black Belt) collectively represent decades of high-level BJJ experience. Fundamentals classes are available for beginners. Competition-prep tracks are available for those who want them.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
        <div class="flex-1 min-h-52 bg-iron/30 border border-iron flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-3">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-smoke/30" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M23 19a2 2 0 01-2 2H3a2 2 0 01-2-2V8a2 2 0 012-2h4l2-3h6l2 3h4a2 2 0 012 2v11z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/><circle cx="12" cy="13" r="4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/></svg>
          <p class="font-mono text-[10px] tracking-widest text-smoke/40 uppercase">Image Coming Soon</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1 min-h-52 bg-iron/30 border border-iron flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-3">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-smoke/30" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M23 19a2 2 0 01-2 2H3a2 2 0 01-2-2V8a2 2 0 012-2h4l2-3h6l2 3h4a2 2 0 012 2v11z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/><circle cx="12" cy="13" r="4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/></svg>
          <p class="font-mono text-[10px] tracking-widest text-smoke/40 uppercase">Image Coming Soon</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Who it is for -->
    <div class="mb-20 max-w-4xl">
      <p class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-smoke border-b border-iron pb-2 mb-8">WHO IT IS FOR</p>
      <ul class="space-y-3 font-body text-canvas/80 leading-relaxed">
        <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-brass font-mono text-xs mt-1 shrink-0">+</span><span>Complete beginners who have never been on a mat</span></li>
        <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-brass font-mono text-xs mt-1 shrink-0">+</span><span>Grapplers from wrestling or judo backgrounds adding submission skills</span></li>
        <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-brass font-mono text-xs mt-1 shrink-0">+</span><span>MMA athletes building a ground game they can rely on</span></li>
        <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-brass font-mono text-xs mt-1 shrink-0">+</span><span>Competition-focused students working toward regional and national events</span></li>
        <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-brass font-mono text-xs mt-1 shrink-0">+</span><span>Anyone who wants a long-term practice with measurable, belt-tracked progress</span></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- 3-image gallery strip -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-24">
      {[1,2,3].map(() => (
        <div class="h-56 bg-iron/30 border border-iron flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-3">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-smoke/30" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M23 19a2 2 0 01-2 2H3a2 2 0 01-2-2V8a2 2 0 012-2h4l2-3h6l2 3h4a2 2 0 012 2v11z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/><circle cx="12" cy="13" r="4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/></svg>
          <p class="font-mono text-[10px] tracking-widest text-smoke/40 uppercase">Image Coming Soon</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

    <!-- What a class looks like -->
    <div class="mb-16 max-w-4xl">
      <p class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-smoke border-b border-iron pb-2 mb-8">WHAT A CLASS LOOKS LIKE</p>
      <p class="font-body text-canvas/80 leading-relaxed">A typical Gi class opens with a warm-up using BJJ-specific movement drills, shrimping, bridging, technical stand-ups. The instructor then covers one to two techniques in detail, building them from basic to contextual. Positional drilling follows, where students train specific scenarios with a partner at controlled resistance. Classes close with live rolling. White belts in fundamentals classes are eased in gradually. Advanced classes roll hard.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Wide image -->
    <div class="w-full h-64 bg-iron/30 border border-iron flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-3 mb-24">
      <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-smoke/30" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M23 19a2 2 0 01-2 2H3a2 2 0 01-2-2V8a2 2 0 012-2h4l2-3h6l2 3h4a2 2 0 012 2v11z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/><circle cx="12" cy="13" r="4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/></svg>
      <p class="font-mono text-[10px] tracking-widest text-smoke/40 uppercase">Image Coming Soon</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Schedule -->
    <div class="mb-16">
      <p class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-smoke border-b border-iron pb-2 mb-8">CLASS SCHEDULE</p>
      <Schedule client:load filterDiscipline="bjj-gi" compact={true} />
    </div>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="border border-iron p-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start sm:items-center justify-between gap-6">
      <div>
        <p class="font-display text-2xl uppercase text-canvas">Try it free.</p>
        <p class="font-mono text-xs text-smoke mt-1">7 days. No commitment.</p>
      </div>
      <a href="/free-trial" class="inline-block bg-brass text-void font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase px-8 py-4 hover:bg-canvas transition-colors duration-200">
        CLAIM FREE TRIAL
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</Base>
